###
Regulation
REGULATION No 03/2016 OF 24/06/2016 ON PUBLICATION BY BANKS OF FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND OTHER DISCLOSURES
Pursuant to Law No 55/2007 of 30/11/2007 governing the Central Bank of Rwanda, especially in articles 5,6,9,17,56, 57 and 58; Pursuant to Law No 007/2008 of 08/04/2008 concerning organization of banking, especially its article 50; The National Bank of Rwanda, hereafter referred to as “Central Bank”, decrees: